inquiries.query:
/*
In the job_postings_fact table get the job_id, job_title_short, job toce, job_via, and salary_year_avg columns.
Only look at jobs that are not posted 'via Linkedin'
*/

SELECT
	job_id,
    job_title_short,
    job_location,
    job_via,
    salary_year_avg
	
FROM 
	job_postings_fact
where
	job_via <> 'via LinkedIn'
inquiries.name: com practice problem-4
